entries.femaleVariant: So... we gonna talk about yesterday?
Oh, I read it. 'Cept there's no mention of me tellin' you to delta the fuck outta there.
Yeah, no biggie. Not like that cyberpsycho was a tank on two chrome legs...
What the fuck were you thinkin'? There's a reason MaxTac exists, ya know...
Civilians were in danger. What was I supposed to do – just watch them get mowed down?
Listen – you, me and every fuckin' cop in this city might as well be a civilian next to MaxTac.
The day they give us the gear they're packin'? Go right ahead, be the hero, save fuckin' the day.
But until then, you keep your head down and listen to me. That understood?
